pageContext.claim: “[Joe Biden] would go to a place, whether it's China or Ukraine, or any place -- Russia. You take a look at what he's done, and his son was like a human vacuum cleaner. They take out millions and millions and millions of dollars, and in some cases, it was like immediate, and in some cases Joe was Vice President -- in many cases -- when this was all happening...The voter has to know that a man who was Vice President was funneling tens of millions of dollars to his family”
pageContext.analysis: Biden’s taxes and financial disclosure forms do not suggest that he has taken any money from foreign governments.
